Place pork medallions in large zip-top freezer bag. Process scallions, habanero peppers, olive oil, lime juice, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and salt in a blender or food processor 20 seconds or until smooth, stopping to scrape down sides. Pour over pork. Seal and chill 2 hours, turning occasionally. Remove pork from marinade, discarding marinade. Grill pork over medium-high heat 2 minutes on each side or to desired degree of doneness.